<title>USA: Time Warner to redeem Turner notes.</title>
<headline>Time Warner to redeem Turner notes.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-01-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Time Warner Inc on Tuesday said it would redeem all of the outstanding convertible liquid yield option notes, due 2007, issued by its Turner Broadcasting System subsidiary.</p>
<p>The company said that the redemption would reduce fully diluted shares outstanding by 5.6 million shares.</p>
<p>Redemption is scheduled for February 13, with the redemption price per $1,000 principal amount set at $490.58.</p>
